fields.title: Canadian Grand Prix
fields.description: We have a great race in Canada coming up! Get up to speed with everything you need to know about the 2023 Canadian Grand Prix, which takes place over 70 laps of the 4.361-kilometre Circuit Gilles-Villeneuve in Montreal on Sunday, June 18.
